<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us | GlobalCare Hospital</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <!-- Font Awesome -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #0d6efd;
      --secondary-color: #00bcd4;
      --accent-color: #ff6b6b;
      --dark-color: #2c3e50;
      --light-color: #f8f9fa;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }

    .about-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
      color: white;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .about-header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: url('https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/medical-background-with-abstract-shapes_53876-93773.jpg') center/cover;
      opacity: 0.1;
    }

    .about-header h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      position: relative;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .about-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      position: relative;
    }

    .about-section {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      margin-top: -40px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .about-section:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .about-section h3 {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--dark-color);
    }

    .about-section h3::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 50px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .mission-values {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .value-box {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .value-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .value-box h5 {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .value-box h5 i {
      margin-right: 10px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .value-box p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .icon-circle {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.1), rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.1));
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
      }

      .about-header {
        padding: 60px 20px;
      }

      .about-section {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include('navbar') %>

    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="about-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About GlobalCare Multispecialty Hospital</h1>
        <p>Excellence in Healthcare. Compassion in Service.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Section -->
    <div class="container my-5">
      <div class="about-section">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-hospital me-2"></i> Who We Are</h3>
        <p>
          GlobalCare Multispecialty Hospital is a premier healthcare institution dedicated to providing world-class
          medical services to patients around the globe. With over two decades of experience, we combine advanced
          medical technologies with a compassionate approach to healing.
        </p>

        <h3><i class="fas fa-bullseye me-2"></i> Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
          To deliver exceptional healthcare services that enhance the quality of life, foster healing, and uphold human
          dignity, regardless of geographic or economic boundaries.
        </p>

        <h3><i class="fas fa-eye me-2"></i> Our Vision</h3>
        <p>
          To be recognized as a global leader in healthcare â€” where innovation meets compassion, and every patient
          matters.
        </p>

        <div class="mission-values">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-heartbeat me-2"></i> Why Choose Us</h3>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="value-box">
                <div class="icon-circle">
                  <i class="fas fa-ambulance"></i>
                </div>
                <h5>24/7 Emergency</h5>
                <p>Always ready with fully equipped trauma and emergency care units for immediate response with average
                  response time under 5 minutes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="value-box">
                <div class="icon-circle">
                  <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
                </div>
                <h5>World-Class Specialists</h5>
                <p>Our team includes 200+ highly skilled doctors and surgeons trained in the world's leading
                  institutions with 98% patient satisfaction rate.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="value-box">
                <div class="icon-circle">
                  <i class="fas fa-microscope"></i>
                </div>
                <h5>Advanced Technology</h5>
                <p>Equipped with cutting-edge diagnostic and surgical tools including robotic surgery systems ensuring
                  precise and efficient care.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('fotter') %>

      <!-- Bootstrap JS Bundle with Popper -->
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>